你所在的团队负责一个日活 200 万的电商平台，后端是 6 台 Go 微服务实例（分两组：商品服务 3 台 10.0.1.{1-3}:8080，订单服务 3 台 10.0.2.{1-3}:9090）。运维新同事刚接手 Nginx 配置，写出了以下反向代理配置并提交了 Code Review：

```nginx
worker_processes auto;
worker_rlimit_nofile 65535;

events {
    worker_connections 16384;
    use epoll;
    multi_accept on;
}

http {
    log_format main '$remote_addr - $remote_user [$time_local] '
                    '"$request" $status $body_bytes_sent '
                    '"$http_referer" "$http_user_agent" '
                    'rt=$request_time uct=$upstream_connect_time '
                    'uht=$upstream_header_time urt=$upstream_response_time '
                    'cache=$upstream_cache_status';

    access_log /var/log/nginx/access.log main buffer=64k flush=5s;

    upstream product_service {
        ip_hash;
        server 10.0.1.1:8080 weight=5 max_fails=3 fail_timeout=30s;
        server 10.0.1.2:8080 weight=5 max_fails=3 fail_timeout=30s;
        server 10.0.1.3:8080 weight=3 max_fails=3 fail_timeout=30s;
        keepalive 32;
    }

    upstream order_service {
        least_conn;
        server 10.0.2.1:9090 max_fails=2 fail_timeout=10s;
        server 10.0.2.2:9090 max_fails=2 fail_timeout=10s;
        server 10.0.2.3:9090 max_fails=2 fail_timeout=10s;
        server 10.0.2.4:9090 backup;
        keepalive 64;
    }

    proxy_cache_path /var/cache/nginx/products levels=1:2
                     keys_zone=product_cache:20m max_size=2g
                     inactive=30m use_temp_path=off;

    server {
        listen 80;
        server_name api.shop.com;
        return 301 https://$host$request_uri;
    }

    server {
        listen 443 ssl http2;
        server_name api.shop.com;

        ssl_certificate     /etc/nginx/ssl/shop.crt;
        ssl_certificate_key /etc/nginx/ssl/shop.key;
        ssl_protocols TLSv1.2 TLSv1.3;
        ssl_ciphers HIGH:!aNULL:!MD5;

        # 商品查询 — 带缓存
        location /api/v1/products {
            proxy_cache product_cache;
            proxy_cache_valid 200 5m;
            proxy_cache_valid 404 30s;
            proxy_cache_key "$scheme$host$request_uri";
            add_header X-Cache-Status $upstream_cache_status;

            proxy_pass http://product_service;
            proxy_http_version 1.1;
            proxy_set_header Connection "";
            proxy_set_header Host $host;
            proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;

            proxy_connect_timeout 3s;
            proxy_read_timeout 10s;
            proxy_send_timeout 5s;

            proxy_buffering on;
            proxy_buffer_size 8k;
            proxy_buffers 16 8k;

            proxy_next_upstream error timeout http_502 http_503;
            proxy_next_upstream_tries 2;
            proxy_next_upstream_timeout 5s;
        }

        # 订单操作 — 无缓存
        location /api/v1/orders {
            proxy_pass http://order_service;
            proxy_http_version 1.1;
            proxy_set_header Connection "";
            proxy_set_header Host $host;
            proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
            proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;

            proxy_connect_timeout 3s;
            proxy_read_timeout 30s;
            proxy_send_timeout 10s;

            proxy_next_upstream error timeout http_502;
            proxy_next_upstream_tries 1;
        }

        location /nginx_status {
            stub_status on;
            allow 10.0.0.0/8;
            deny all;
        }
    }
}
```

运行 `nginx -T` 确认配置已加载后，你在 Review 中发现了几个问题。请回答以下问题：

1. `ip_hash` 用在商品服务的 upstream 上合适吗？它和 `round-robin`（默认）、`least_conn`、`hash $request_uri consistent` 各自的适用场景是什么？
2. `proxy_cache` 缓存商品查询的策略有什么潜在风险？`proxy_cache_key` 该怎么设计才能避免缓存穿透和缓存污染？
3. 订单服务的 `proxy_next_upstream` 配置了 `error timeout http_502`，对 POST 请求做自动重试是否安全？如何限制只对幂等请求重试？
4. `keepalive 32` / `keepalive 64` 这两个值是否合理？keepalive 连接数应该怎么估算？
5. 三组超时参数（connect/read/send）的设置有什么讲究？商品服务 `proxy_read_timeout 10s` 和订单服务 `proxy_read_timeout 30s` 的差异反映了什么设计考量？
6. 这份配置缺少了哪些生产必备的优化项（如 proxy_buffering 细节、gzip 压缩、限流、安全头）？
